回家的感觉很好
Feels good to be home.

1495
01:33:23,090 --> 01:33:26,120
中间那个人就是他 他和他女儿
And that's him in the middle. Him and the girl.

1496
01:33:28,220 --> 01:33:29,690
再见 法兰克叔叔 爱你
Good night, Uncle Frank. Love you!

1497
01:33:29,690 --> 01:33:30,860
好的 法兰克
Okay, Frankie!

1498
01:34:00,560 --> 01:34:02,830
爸爸 厨房打扫干净了 我要去睡了
Dad, the kitchen's clean. I'm going to bed.

1499
01:34:05,130 --> 01:34:06,430
好的 孩子
Okay, honey.

1500
01:34:10,130 --> 01:34:12,970
喂 你能帮我一下吗
Hey, can you help me with this?

1501
01:34:12,970 --> 01:34:14,470
- 挪动一点点  - 挪动它？
- Move this? - Slide it down a little.

1502
01:34:14,470 --> 01:34:15,640
是的 就一点点
Yeah, just a little bit. Mmm-hmm.

1503
01:34:15,640 --> 01:34:16,770
为什么要挪动它
Why are you moving this?

1504
01:34:16,770 --> 01:34:19,610
因为我要你到这里来
Because I need you to come over here.

1505
01:34:19,610 --> 01:34:21,240
我刚看到有个人经过
I just saw somebody run by.

1506
01:34:21,240 --> 01:34:23,010
什么人经过？
What do you mean you just saw someone run by?

1507
01:34:23,010 --> 01:34:25,150
- 你看到有人经过这里？ - 是的 是的
- You saw someone run by here? - Yeah, I did. I did.

1508
01:34:25,150 --> 01:34:26,610
我要你到楼梯下
I want you to get under the stairs.

1509
01:34:26,620 --> 01:34:27,980
爸爸 你为什么让我到楼梯下
Dad, why are you putting me under the stairs?

1510
01:34:27,980 --> 01:34:30,350
- 马上打电话报警 - 爸爸一定要小心
- Call the cops right now. - Dad, please be careful.

1511
01:34:30,350 --> 01:34:32,150
- 用你的手机报警 - 爸爸 拜托
- Take your phone and dial 911. - Dad, please!

1512
01:34:37,860 --> 01:34:39,430
911勤务中心 你有什么麻烦？
911, what is your emergency?

1513
01:34:39,430 --> 01:34:40,760
有人正要闯进我家
There's men, they're breaking into my house.

1514
01:34:40,760 --> 01:34:41,930
他们在我家的草坪上
They're on my front lawn.

1515
01:34:41,930 --> 01:34:43,000
好像是来杀我的
I think they're coming to kill me.

1516
01:34:43,000 --> 01:34:44,130
我叫乔丹·科尔西
My name is Jordan Kersey.

1517
01:34:44,130 --> 01:34:47,140
我在艾文思顿的多塞特路20号
I'm at 20 Dorset Road in Evanston.

1518
01:34:47,140 --> 01:34:48,340
他们好像进来了
I think they're here.

1519
01:36:18,300 --> 01:36:20,130
乔丹 我没事
Jordan, I'm okay.

1520
01:36:20,130 --> 01:36:21,800
