Dad. Dad!

1521
01:36:21,800 --> 01:36:25,630
安静 等着警察来
Stay quiet. Just wait for the police.

1522
01:36:25,640 --> 01:36:28,410
不要出来 留在里面
Do not come out. Stay in there.

1523
01:37:14,280 --> 01:37:16,120
坐下
Sit down.

1524
01:37:16,120 --> 01:37:17,290
爸爸
Dad?

1525
01:37:18,790 --> 01:37:20,420
他们好像刚打中了我爸
I think they just shot my dad.

1526
01:37:20,420 --> 01:37:23,160
爸爸 爸爸
Dad! Dad!

1527
01:37:23,160 --> 01:37:25,160
乔丹 留在那里
Jordan, just stay up there!

1528
01:37:25,160 --> 01:37:28,160
是你女儿吗
Is that your little girl?

1529
01:37:28,170 --> 01:37:30,530
你听说过有人被烧死吗
Now, you ever hear someone burn to death?

1530
01:37:31,630 --> 01:37:33,330
会让你满意的 科尔西医生
You're in for a treat, Dr. Kersey.

1531
01:37:33,340 --> 01:37:34,500
爸爸
Dad!

1532
01:38:01,830 --> 01:38:04,730
你是说你手上的
So you're saying you got both the cut

1533
01:38:04,730 --> 01:38:07,330
基本痊愈的伤口
on your hand that's almost healed

1534
01:38:07,340 --> 01:38:10,910
和肩膀上的伤口都是今晚的伤 是这样吗
and the shot in the shoulder tonight? That's your story.

1535
01:38:10,910 --> 01:38:13,640
这是事实 是这样的
That's what happened. That's my story.

1536
01:38:13,640 --> 01:38:15,210
嗯
Hmm.

1537
01:38:15,210 --> 01:38:19,310
手枪和步枪的许可证呢
And the paperwork for the pistols and the rifle?

1538
01:38:19,320 --> 01:38:21,920
你可以给海盗旗体育用品店打电话
You can call Jolly Roger's Sporting Goods.

1539
01:38:21,920 --> 01:38:23,390
找费雪妮问问
Ask for Bethany.

1540
01:38:23,390 --> 01:38:26,750
你买这些枪都是在…
And you bought these guns...

1541
01:38:26,760 --> 01:38:29,920
我女儿回家的那一天
The day my daughter came home.

1542
01:38:29,930 --> 01:38:33,100
只为了应对万一再发生这样的事
Just in case something like this ever happened again.

1543
01:38:34,230 --> 01:38:36,600
有把克拉克手枪吗
What about a Glock?

1544
01:38:36,600 --> 01:38:41,000
我之前有一把 后来决定把它扔了
I had one for a while. Decided to get rid of it.

1545
01:38:42,170 --> 01:38:43,570
早就没了？
Gone for good?

1546
01:38:44,880 --> 01:38:46,940
是的 早就没了
Yeah. Gone for good.

1547
01:38:49,350 --> 01:38:52,050
我没别的问题了
Well, I got everything I need.

1548
01:38:52,050 --> 01:38:54,450
看起来案情很简单 诺克斯回来了
Seems pretty straightforward. Knox came back,

1549
01:38:54,450 --> 01:38:56,720
