Have I told you how proud I am with you?

1568
01:40:12,580 --> 01:40:15,740
是的 爸爸 你对我说过无数次了
Yes, Dad, you've told me, like, a billion times.

1569
01:40:15,750 --> 01:40:18,350
如果你需要什么 我就在三站之外
If you ever need anything, I'm just three stops away.

1570
01:40:18,350 --> 01:40:20,890
我知道 爸爸 我有你的号码
I know, Dad. I've got the number.

1571
